{"tid":2115834,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【認暴動罪】還柙青年阿均獄中信：遇見大隻勇武、書生手足，都係有血有肉嘅人","createTime":"2020-07-19T18:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T13:37:52.000Z","uid":202425,"like":89,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"82ebe9862dd5272fc17efe8f7ad8d5f5bb8bdc43","tid":2115834,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T18:45:32.000Z","msg":"全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WzRiwy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WzRiwy&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=0013bbd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WzRiwy</a><br />\n<br />\n【身在赤柱監獄】去年7月28日，有44人被指在上環干犯暴動罪，25歲的阿均（化名）是其中一位。今年5月尾，他於庭上表示擬認罪並要求取消保釋，至今已還柙近2個月。阿均回信眾新聞講述近況以及對港區國安法的看法。<br />\n<br />\n阿均說，在獄中遇到形形式式的人，譬如跟大隻「真勇武」練體能、遇到讀政政（政治與行政學系）的本土派跟他分享《金剛經》。6月底，他從荔枝角收押所被調到赤柱監獄：「中間隔咗十幾日先再收到家書，嗰段日子，雖然我表面冇嘢，但我內心係幾崩潰。」至於國安法，他說「樂見」攬炒，並籲打好文宣戰。<br />\n<br />\n【全文閱讀】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WzRiwy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WzRiwy&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=0013bbd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WzRiwy</a><br />\n－－－－－－－－<br />\n亼 緊貼眾新聞 亼<br />\nFollow TG：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkcnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkcnews&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=311c6aad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkcnews</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zykNXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zykNXc&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=12cfaa75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zykNXc</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37AfYcp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37AfYcp&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=a634252d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37AfYcp</a><br />\nYouTube：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37A1PMI\" da